希里安·墨菲表示他“可以”出演《28年后》续集https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-available-for-28-days-later-sequel-3583215?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cillian-murphy-available-for-28-days-后期续集Alex BerryTue, 06 Feb 2024 12:21:06 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3583215 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>后世界末日系列的第三部分正在开发中</p><p>希里安<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-available-for-28-days-later-sequel-3583215">·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 表示他“可以”出演《28 年之后》续集，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Cillian-Murphy-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy)</a>透露，他“可以”出演《惊变<em>28 天》</em>的续集。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/1951281-1951281">《T2 猜火车》——电影评论</a></strong></li></ul><p>作为<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=thHyKiVcWOM" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SAG-AFTRA 基金会对话</a>计划的一部分，墨菲用 90 分钟的时间讲述了他在舞台和银幕上令人印象深刻的职业生涯。这段对话于 12 月录制，还涵盖了他在丹尼·博伊尔的后世界末日恐怖片<em>《惊变 28 天》</em>中的工作。</p><p>该片于 2002 年上映，由亚历克斯·加兰编剧，墨菲饰演一名自行车快递员，他从昏迷中醒来，发现一种高度传染性的病毒导致了社会崩溃。</p><p>续集《惊变<em>28 周》</em>于 2008 年上映，重点讲述了原片事件的后果，涉及破碎的英国的恢复和复兴。由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idris-elba">伊德里斯·艾尔巴</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeremy-renner">杰瑞米·雷纳</a>和罗伯特·卡莱尔主演的该片也获得了好评。 </p><figure id="attachment_3583221" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3583221" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3583221" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/28-Days-Later.jpg" alt="28天后" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/28-Days-Later.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/28-Days-Later-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/28-Days-Later-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/28-Days-Later-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/28-Days-Later-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/28-Days-Later-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3583221" class="wp-caption-text">导演丹尼·博伊尔、娜奥米·哈里斯、希里安·墨菲和制片人安德鲁·麦克唐纳出席《惊变 28 天》在英国伦敦举行的首映式。图片来源：Getty Images/摄影：Yui Mok – PA Images/PA Images via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>上个月，有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/28-years-later-in-development-danny-boyle-to-direct-3568935">消息称第三部电影</a><em>《28年后》</em>正在开发中。博伊尔和加兰都将回归，据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/cillian-murphy-28-days-later-available-sequel-1235896054/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》报道</em></a>，墨菲将担任执行制片人。</p><p>当墨菲被告知续集的前景时，考虑到他的角色幸存下来，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>奥本海默</em></a>明星说：“我可以。”</p><p>由娜奥米·哈里斯、布莱丹·格里森和克里斯托弗·埃克莱斯顿主演的<em>《惊变 28 天》在商业和评论上都</em>取得了成功。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/covid">COVID-19 大流行</a>期间，这部电影产生了更大的文化影响，因为国家封锁令在电影的开场序列中模仿了这些特征。</p><p>关于这种影响，墨菲说：“在<em>《惊变 28 天》大</em>流行期间，每个人给我发送的表情包数量——我确实知道什么是表情包——太疯狂了。”</p><p>他补充道：“这只是表明好的写作是有先见之明的，它总是有先见之明和相对的。”</p><p>此外，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-new-movie-berlin-film-festival-3573195">墨菲即将上映的电影将为 2 月 15 日至 25 日举行的柏林国际电影节拉开帷幕</a>。</p><p>希里安<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-available-for-28-days-later-sequel-3583215">·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 表示他“可以”出演《28 年之后》续集，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Arctic Monkeys 的 Matt Helders 在 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼上会见了 Spice Girls 的 Mel C，他表示这“弥补”了“被剥夺一到三个格莱美奖” https://www.nme.com/news/music/arctic-monkeys-matt-helders-met-spice-girls-mel-c-at-grammys-2024-said-it-makes-up-for-being-抢劫了格莱美或三-3583187？utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=arctic-monkeys-matt-helders-met-spice-girls-mel-c-at-grammys-2024-said-it-makes-准备被剥夺一到三项格莱美奖Damian JonesTue, 06 Feb 2024 12:07:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3583187 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Arctic Monkeys 鼓手 Matt Helders 和 Mel C" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>谢菲尔德乐队当晚错过了 Boygenius 和 Paramore</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/arctic-monkeys-matt-helders-met-spice-girls-mel-c-at-grammys-2024-said-it-makes-up-for-being-robbed-of-a-grammy-or-three-3583187">北极猴子乐团 (Arctic Monkeys) 的马特·赫尔德斯 (Matt Helders) 在 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼上与辣妹组合 (Spice Girls) 的梅尔·C (Mel C) 会面后表示，这“弥补”了“被剥夺一到三个格莱美奖”的消息，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Arctic Monkeys 鼓手 Matt Helders 和 Mel C" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2024_matthelders_melc_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Monkeys</a>鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matt-helders">马特·赫尔德斯 (Matt Helders)</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼</a>上与辣妹组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mel-c-says-spice-girls-are-always-working-on-a-reunion-with-victoria-beckham-3323680">(Spice Girls)</a>歌手梅尔· <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/melanie-c">C (Mel C)</a>见面后，对她进行了赞扬，称这弥补了“被剥夺一到三个格莱美奖”的遗憾。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/arctic-monkeys-stadium-tour-uk-glastonbury-2023-3447907">为什么 Arctic Monkeys 的 2023 年体育场巡演标志着乐队的新黄金时代</a></strong></li></ul><p>这支谢菲尔德摇滚乐队当晚角逐三项大奖，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/arctic-monkeys-the-car-review-3330197">《The Car》</a>的最佳另类音乐专辑奖、最佳另类音乐表演奖和最佳摇滚表演奖，但后来输给了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">Boygenius</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a> 。</p><p>在颁奖典礼上，赫尔德斯和他的妻子阿曼达·布兰克 (Amanda Blank) 撞见了梅尔·C (Mel C)，并对辣妹表示欢迎。</p><p>这位 Monkeys 鼓手在他妻子的 Instagram Stories 上发布了一张与她的合影，并说道：“我可能被剥夺了一三个格莱美奖，但我遇到了运动香料，这弥补了一切，我的妻子见到她时哭了。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2-S1XKulQ2/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_camp